text: Ivo Felix (born 4 December 1955) is a Czech ski jumper. He competed in the normal hill event at the 1976 Winter Olympics. ==References== Category:1955 births Category:Living people Category:Czech male ski jumpers Category:Olympic ski jumpers of Czechoslovakia Category:Ski jumpers at the 1976 Winter Olympics Category:People from Jilemnice
